        "jsonBody": "{\"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"max_tokens\": 1024, \"messages\": [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"너는 투자 의견 종합자다. 3 전문가 의견을 받아 최종 판단.\\n\\n종목: {{$json.ticker}}\\n\\n[가격]  score {{$json.p_score}} | {{$json.p_reason}}\\n[뉴스]  score {{$json.n_score}} | {{$json.n_reason}}\\n[차트]  score {{$json.c_score}} | {{$json.c_reason}}\\n\\nJSON만:\\n{\\n  \\\"verdict\\\": \\\"BUY_STRONG|BUY_WEAK|HOLD|SELL_WEAK|SELL_STRONG\\\",\\n  \\\"agreement\\\": \\\"all_agree|2of3|disagree\\\",\\n  \\\"summary\\\": \\\"2~3문장 종합 의견\\\"\\n}\"}]}",
